# Hiring proxy token — a single credential valid for both Anthropic and OpenAI
# via the proxy (D-010). SERVER-SIDE ONLY.
#
#   - NEVER prefix it NEXT_PUBLIC_.
#   - NEVER import it into a client component.
#   - NEVER commit the real value. Put it in .env.local (gitignored) locally,
#     and in Vercel's encrypted env-var settings for production.
#
# This file (.env.example) is tracked and must contain the NAME ONLY, no value.
PROXY_TOKEN=
